{
  "stem": "6526.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we came to Waldenburg, it was evening.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had to go-- they did not have a place where to put us in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a mine in Waldenburg.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What kind of mine it was, I don't know, but they pushed us into the mine and closed the door.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were there, a few thousand of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And from the heat, and the smell, and the-- and the-- whatever it was, many of us died in that-- in that thing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When we came out there, I took my two friends that we got together, one as well was-- looked like me, like my brother, also blonde, and a friend of his-- excuse me for the expression, they peed in their pants.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They made in their-- terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Coming down from-- there was a little lake.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I washed them up, I cleaned them up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there were all the civilians, civilian workers and prisoners of war, French prisoners of war were there also.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I don't know things, because the French I could recognize their language they were talking.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And civilian workers, Poles and French.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they [INAUDIBLE] civilian workers, also on a march to go away, but not under the German supervision.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went out to beg from the civilian workers to give us some bread.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Who supervised them?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Under what--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't need any supervision because they were free.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were not under the--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the Latvians, and by the Ukrainians, by the Lithuanians and by the Poles.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were under the German rule.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were under, under the German contract.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, they were Volksdeutsche maybe or--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went to the civilians, the French or the other ones, and begged them for bread or other things.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I brought it to my friends and myself.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
